actions.text: Referred to the House Committee on Financial Services.

official_title: To revise the quorum requirement for the Board of Directors of the Export-Import Bank of the United States.
subjects: Export-Import Bank of the United States

summary.text: This bill amends the Export-Import Bank Act of 1945 to revise the quorum requirement for the Board of Directors of the Export-Import Bank of the United States to require the lesser of three members or the number of members holding office on the board (currently, at least three members) for there to be a quorum.
